Blocks.Text: We proposed CARLANE, the first 3-way sim-to-real domain adaptation
The current difficulties of the examined UDA methods to adequately align the
source and target domains confirm the need for the proposed CARLANE
UDA methods should be tested with care and under the right conditions on a full-
scale car. However, real-world testing in the model vehicle domain can be carried
out in a safe and controlled environment.
